<h2>Implementation of The Bellman-Ford Algorithm</h2>
<p>Implementing the Bellman-Ford algorithm is very similar to <a href=3D"ht=
tps://www.w3schools.com/dsa/dsa_algo_graphs_dijkstra.php#dijkstraImpl">how =
we implemented Dijkstra's algorithm</a>.</p>
<p>We start by creating the <code class=3D"w3-codespan">Graph</code> class,=
 where the methods <code class=3D"w3-codespan">__init__</code>, <code class=
=3D"w3-codespan">add_edge</code>, and <code class=3D"w3-codespan">add_verte=
x</code> will be used to create the specific graph we want to run the Bellm=
an-Ford algorithm on to find the shortest paths.</p>
